column5: Haven't seen him on here for a good while. Just wondering if every thing was ok and big cliff also.
Noticed that the other day... one of the few that has had his account decommissioned! Maybe his Toyota broke down for good ...  Big Cliff's around..
A few of the guys are simply in the shadows these days. Not much on OFC that catches their interest.
And i wonder what will be said of me someday behind my back........some classless posts here, congratulations......   Tom.....BB is fine. I can get you in contact if you like. PM me.
Im sure its not behind anyones back. After all they are still here lurking everyday.
Does it really matter Paul? I don,t care what people say about me.Really I don,t.

What other people think of me is none of my business... Read that somewhere, seems to make a lot of sense to me... that said, I really do hope that BB and Hillary are doing well! There's a ton of Lake Erie perch waiting on him! HH
